casebody.head_matter:
In the Matter of DISCIPLINE OF Gerald Isadore KATZ.
No. D-2851.
Supreme Court of the United States
Nov. 2, 2015.
Gerald Isadore Katz, of Bethesda, Maryland, is suspended from the practice of law in this Court and a rule will issue, returnable within 40 days, requiring him to show cause why he should not be disbarred from the practice of law in this Court.
